D&h=a1cc55a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mathsmutt.co.uk/files/newt.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T22:07:59.000Z","msg":"佢話係就係，based on 你唔識就信？標題擺明鳩改<br />\nNewton&rsquo;s 3 Laws of Motion 係dynamics 講force，解釋佢哋會點變；SUVAT 呢組最簡單嘅 equation of motion 係 kinematics 講郁動，唔需要理點解"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T22:12:36.000Z","msg":"[edit] #1 跟個post 標題講 Newtonian Mechanics 就冇問題"},{"pid":"c15d842b8aa9a177eebc16542f5e8bd275e7a8c6","tid":2273130,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b026e96fdf2ebacb52292b9a5eaabab69410aad2","tid":2273130,"uid":244889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e758f292b098c53c7937605c57b239ae9dd9a2b2","tid":2273130,"uid":155902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"樓主呢條係牛頓力學formula 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係constant acceleration 得出既displacement formula"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:40:32.000Z","msg":"Acceleration 唔係mechanics係咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T22:31:07.000Z","msg":"佢即係提下唔 exactly 關牛頓或者之後成個mechanics (dynamics) 事，嚴格嚟講只係個起點，根據個例子答 hyperbolic motion 已經得"},{"pid":"dc35559336cb6269c7ed077d797e361c03d0c0d8","tid":2273130,"uid":337240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a533182e345e1a9c44001ee79112802d5995f19","tid":2273130,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e758f292b098c53c7937605c57b239ae9dd9a2b2","tid":2273130,"uid":155902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"樓主呢條係牛頓力學formula 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個係constant acceleration 得出既displacement formula"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T16:37:17.000Z","msg":"條式個a就係F=ma個a喎<br />\n<br />\n即係條式係based on成套牛頓理論嘅必然結果喎<br />\n<br />\nbtw google完先知條式叫Newton's Law of motion<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.mathsmutt.co.uk/files/newt.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mathsmutt.co.uk%2Ffiles%2Fnewt.htm&d=RNNv2si1j6MvuJ657i5J8nlPKE5%2BvOhv5kPCmhOEeDs%3D&h=a1cc55a5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.mathsmutt.co.uk/files/newt.htm</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T22:32:16.000Z","msg":"咁就算special relativity都可以有個a嘅<br />\n<br />\n單單討論速度/加速度只能算係kinematics<br />\n用中文可能會易明，kinematics=運動學，mechanics=力學<br />\nkinematics唔討論force,只討論motion,<br />\n力學就真係講力<br />\n<br />\n咁牛頓力學條F=ma就係連繫力同加速度嘅關係，將mechanics連繫到kinematics<br />\n<br />\n你講嗰條式係一條同牛頓力學無關，係kinematics嘅式。佢係描述緊<strong>given</strong> constant acceleration下嘅motion<br />\n<br />\n但係我地唔知到個constant acceleration係點嚟。<br />\nnewtoian下物件係constant force下就係constant acceleration，就可以用嗰條式。但係newtonian通常情況下都唔一定係constant acceleration<br />\n<br />\n倒不如話你嗰條式係<br />\nv=s'(t), a=v'(t)=constant, s(0)=0, v(0)=0<br />\n嘅solution。牛頓又好，狹義廣義又好，只要出現以上condition都係依個結果。同你咩力學係冇關係"},{"pid":"02c423ca9eb7c37af01939b18832d31437dd14a4","tid":2273130,"uid":337240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T22:47:00.000Z","msg":"咁講番牛頓力學係唔係有所謂相對論版<br />\n<br />\n你可以簡單理解為相對論係一個較為&rdquo;大&rdquo;嘅理，可以話包括咗牛頓力學在內。你又可以話牛頓力學係唔準確<br />\n<br />\n係低密度同低速下，相對論可以簡化，以及可以用牛頓力學去近似<br />\n例如所謂牛頓重力都只係愛因斯坦場方程式嘅一個limit。如果叫狹義相對論版本嘅&ldquo;F=ma&ldquo;，其實可以話係反轉咗。應該話係牛頓版嘅F=dp/dt。<br />\n<br />\n因為相對論係一個較&ldquo;大&rdquo;嘅理論，牛頓力學只係佢嘅一個limit，所以牛頓有嘅，相對論會有(不過可以複雜好多同溝埋咗)，相對論有，牛頓唔一定有"},{"pid":"8e3d3496682460dafcca31b3af91354a64fbaad9","tid":2273130,"uid":323922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dc35559336cb6269c7ed077d797e361c03d0c0d8","tid":2273130,"uid":337240,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a533182e345e1a9c44001ee79112802d5995f19","tid":2273130,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"e758f292b098c53c7937605c57b239ae9dd9a2b2","tid":2273130,"uid":155902,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T15:35:23.000Z","msg":"樓主呢條係牛頓力學formula 咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br /